metadata.name: notable humanity
metadata.description:
Funds routed directly to Doctors Without Borders via The Giving Block for crisis relief in the wake of the earthquake in Turkey and Syria. (Foundation doesn't allow 100% rerouting, so 1% is going to our wallet and will be transferred manually after the auction ends. Proof will be shared on Twitter and Discord.)

notables is an art x social signalling collection, inspired by the social meta-layer construct and underlying status game of web3.

notables begins with a set of 83 genesis 1/1's on BTC (ordinals), with an associated ETH [r̶e̶d̶a̶c̶t̶e̶d̶]. notables will be the first collection to do this.

The winner of this auction also wins a special black edition from the 83 genesis 1/1's on BTC (ordinals).
